1makua tavva ataniup uqalauqtangit jiriᒤamut pilisᑍnimiut pillugit ᐰru unatarialauqtinnagu gaajamiunik.
2“imaak ataniq uqaqpuq:
3qimmiqjuat pangaliktut qikirrangit tusaqsauliqpata,
4ulluq nalliutingmat pilisᑍnimiut nunguraqtauviksangat,
5gaajamiut qiksaangnirngmut nuᔧjaqsimaniaqput,
6uqaqpusi, ‘ataniup savigjuanga
7qanuqli nuqqangatuinnarunnaqpaa,
